items.title: John F. Kennedy completes Builder’s Sea Trials, First Underway

Kennedy (CVN 79) and her crew departed HII’s Newport News Shipbuilding (NNS) and steamed to sea for the first time for Builder’s Sea Trials, Jan. 28, 2026.
